{"word":"G4334 - προσέρχομαι - prosérchomai - pros-er'-khom-ahee - Come","slug":"G4334","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prosérchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-er'-khom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - proserchomai</b> - <i>pros-er'-khom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a> (including its alternate); to <i>approach</i>, that is, (literally) <i>come near</i>, <i>visit</i>, or (figuratively) <i>worship</i>, <i>assent to:</i> - (as soon as he) come (unto), come thereunto, consent, draw near, go (near, to, unto)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565\">G565</a>"}]}